title: 12/27/21 DPS Hour 3 NFL Week 16 Wrap-Up And Week 17 Preview
itunes:title: 12/27/21 DPS Hour 3 NFL Week 16 Wrap-Up And Week 17 Preview
description:
Jason & Geoff talk about tonight’s game between Miami & New Orleans, and whether or not Tua is the Dolphins quarterback of the future. What to make of this year’s bowl season with opt outs and coaching changes, a look ahead to Week 17 in the NFL, and more!
